OL,6,FChild Sexual Exploitation Supervisor
OL,7,FDetective Sergeant Sophie Draycott
OL,8,Fsaid:
OL,10,F"This has been a long investigation
OL,11,Fwhich revealed Stevenson has been
OL,12,Fcommunicating with children in a
OL,13,Fsexual manner right across the country.
OL,15,F"His behaviour was appalling and
OL,16,Frepeated so I am pleased that he has
OL,17,Fnow been brought to justice for his
OL,18,Fcrimes and is serving a prison
OL,19,Fsentence.
