OL,6,F"I'd also like to thank all the
OL,7,Fvictims for their bravery and support
OL,8,Fthroughout the case.
OL,10,F"Now that social media is such a
OL,11,Fmassive part of our society, I'd
OL,12,Fencourage all parents to please be
OL,13,Faware of who their children are
OL,14,Fcommunicating with online, urge them
OL,15,Fto make sure they are not sending any
OL,16,Fimages to anyone and let their
OL,17,Fchildren know that if they do receive
